# PHPUnit 10 conventions

- Tests at `<slug>/tests/<Class>Test.php`, namespace `<NS>\<Sub>\Tests\…`.
- `bootstrap="vendor/autoload.php"`, `failOnWarning="true"`, `cacheDirectory=".phpunit.cache"` (see `candy-core/phpunit.xml`). Every public method ≥1 test.

Patterns (`sugar-bits/tests/`, `candy-core/tests/`, `candy-vt/tests/`):
- **Snapshot byte** — assert raw `\x1b[1m`-style SGR strings from `view()`. Don't abstract.
- **Golden render** — `<slug>/tests/GoldenRenderTest.php` asserts byte-exact `view()`/`render()` output against committed `<slug>/tests/fixtures/*.golden` files via `SugarCraft\Testing\Snapshot\Assertions::assertGoldenAnsi($path, $output)`. Needs `sugarcraft/candy-testing` dev-dep + path-repo (canonical `sugar-charts/tests/GoldenRenderTest.php`).
- **Snapshot cell-grid** — drive through `SugarCraft\Vt\Terminal\Terminal`, assert `$term->screen()->cell($r,$c)` (`$screen->cols`/`rows` are properties).
- **Behaviour** — drive `update()` with scripted `KeyMsg`/`MouseMsg`, assert `[Model, ?Cmd]`.
- **Coercion** — negative/oversized index, empty, null; assert clamp/no-op.

**Stream-write gotcha**: don't `ftruncate; rewind;` between writes. Slice deltas with `ftell`/`fseek`/`stream_get_contents` (canonical `candy-core/tests/RendererTest.php`).

**FFI** (`candy-pty/tests/`): structural tests run unconditionally; syscall round-trips call `requirePtySyscalls()` first.

Run: `cd <slug> && composer install && vendor/bin/phpunit`.
